name: places/ChIJh0XICQMZ2jERc-RPjdU9KKo/reviews/ChdDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTUNRanFqMHpRRRAB
text: {'text': 'Fantastic display of music and light. We arrived with plenty of time to get a good seat under the tree groves. The nighttime display was truly enjoyable with great music selection and amazing colors. This is a must visit when visiting Singapore.', 'languageCode': 'en'}

name: places/ChIJh0XICQMZ2jERc-RPjdU9KKo/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnTURnLWFMVk53EAE
text: {'text': 'I spent 10 hours out of the Gardens today and saw all five of the paid attractions plus a match of the free areas of the garden.  I did not even know about the show, but had planned to stay to see what all of the Supertrees look like at night time.  I just happened to be there for the 7:45 show.  It was so incredible that I went to a different location to watch the 8:45 show as well.  Planning to go back one evening to schedule being up in the skywalk or observation area during the show.  That must be even more magical.', 'languageCode': 'en'}
